## üó∫Ô∏è Project Roadmap (The Learning Path)

### Phase 1: The Foundation (React 101)
*   Setup Next.js & Tailwind.
*   Understanding Components: Breaking the UI into chunks (Navbar, Hero, Section).
*   Basic Styling: "Making it look good static".

### Phase 2: The Dimension (3D World)
*   Intro to React Three Fiber.
*   Loading a glorious Headphone model (GLTF).
*   Lighting & Environment (The "Studio Setup").

### Phase 3: The Magic (Animation)
*   Connecting Scroll to Animation (GSAP ScrollTrigger).
*   Moving the camera around the headset as user scrolls.
*   Exploding the view (parts separation).

### Phase 4: The Polish (Micro-interactions)
*   Custom smooth cursor.
*   Hover effects.
*   Loading screen.

